description:
Data was generated from file metadata information from the GDC archive release 14, December 2018. Deprecated google cloud storage paths are mapped to file gdc ids. 
More details: https://docs.gdc.cancer.gov/Data/Release_Notes/Data_Release_Notes/#data-release-140
friendlyName: GDC FILE ID TO GCS URLS REL14

fields.description: Unique GDC identifier for this file (corresponds to the file_barcode)  --  this can be used to access more information from the GDC data portal like this: https://portal.gdc.cancer.gov/files/c21b332c-06c6-4403-9032-f91c8f407ba2
fields.name: file_gdc_id

fields.description: Google Cloud Storage (GCS) location ID. Example: gs://gdc-TCGA-phs000178-open/9c4b1b5c-b5cf-48f6-bf41-047ceb8c883c/TCGA-CR-7365-01A-01-TS1.811bb2b7-66e3-4694-891b-10b436ec300d.svs
fields.name: file_gcs_url
